001;page-break-after:avoid;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#4f81bd;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:13pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;font-style:normal">CAREER OBJECTIVE</span></h2><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">Motivated and detail-oriented Electronics and Communication Engineering graduate seeking an entry-level position in a reputed organization where I can apply my technical knowledge in embedded systems, IoT, and programming while gaining practical industry experience and contributing to organizational growth.</span></p><h2 style="padding-top:10pt;margin:0;color:#4f81bd;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:13pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.1500000000000001;page-break-after:avoid;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#4f81bd;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:13pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;font-style:normal">EDUCATION</span></h2><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">Bachelor of Engineering (Electronics and Communication Engineering)</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">University College of Engineering, Kancheepuram</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">CGPA: 8.00</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">HSC: 88.2% | SSLC: 81.5%</span></p><h2 style="padding-top:10pt;margin:0;color:#4f81bd;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:13pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.1500000000000001;page-break-after:avoid;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#4f81bd;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:13pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;font-style:normal">TECHNICAL SKILLS</span></h2><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">Programming: Python</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">Embedded Systems: Microcontrollers, Sensor Interfacing</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">IoT Platforms: ThingSpeak Cloud</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">Tools &amp; Concepts: Image Processing, OCR, Cloud Deployment</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">Software: MS Office</span></p><h2 style="padding-top:10pt;margin:0;color:#4f81bd;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:13pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.1500000000000001;page-break-after:avoid;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#4f81bd;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:13pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;font-style:normal">ACADEMIC PROJECT</span></h2><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">Vehicle Number Plate Detection System</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">- Developed an automated number plate detection system using image processing and OCR with 98% accuracy.</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">- Improved processing efficiency by deploying the system on cloud infrastructure.</span></p><h2 style="padding-top:10pt;margin:0;color:#4f81bd;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:13pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.1500000000000001;page-break-after:avoid;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#4f81bd;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:13pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;font-style:normal">INTERNSHIP</span></h2><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">Intern ŌĆō GB Tech Corp, Chennai (06/2025 ŌĆō 07/2025)</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">- Developed IoT-based temperature and humidity monitoring system using DHT11 and ESP8266.</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">- Implemented real-time data upload and dashboard visualization using ThingSpeak.</span></p><h2 style="padding-top:10pt;margin:0;color:#4f81bd;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:13pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.1500000000000001;page-break-after:avoid;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#4f81bd;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:13pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;font-style:normal">STRENGTHS</span></h2><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">ŌĆó Quick Learner</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">ŌĆó Team Player</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">ŌĆó Problem Solving Ability</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">ŌĆó Good Communication Skills</span></p><h2 style="padding-top:10pt;margin:0;color:#4f81bd;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:13pt;padding-bottom:0pt;line-height:1.1500000000000001;page-break-after:avoid;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#4f81bd;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:13pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;;font-style:normal">DECLARATION</span></h2><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:10pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;line-height:1.1500000000000001;orphans:2;widows:2;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Cambria&quot;;font-style:normal">I hereby declare that the above information is true and correct to the best of my knowledge.</span></p></div></div></div></div></body></html>
